  <h2>Key Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Go 1.25 with minimal standard library usage (~221 lines)</li>
    <li>chi/v5 router for high-performance HTTP routing</li>
    <li>pgx/v5 with pgxpool for efficient PostgreSQL connection pooling</li>
    <li>PostgreSQL stored procedures for server-side business logic</li>
    <li>Extreme throughput under strict resource constraints</li>
  </ul>

